cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SD, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the detection of automated social media bots, which falls under the category of social media analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for detection, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of random string detection could also fall under cs.SD (Software Engineering) or cs.CL (Computation and Language).
